-----------------------
= Rasdaman systemtest =
-----------------------

This directory holds the rasdaman systemtest. By default the test depends on
several tools and services running:
 - rasdaman (compiled with netcdf support)
 - postgres
 - gdal


-------------
= Execution =
-------------

To run the systemtest, execute in this directory:

  make check

By default this will run all test_*/test.sh scripts in the following dirs:

  testcases_fixed
  testcases_mandatory
  testcases_open
  testcases_services (if petascope is installed and available)
